        <item>
            <title>House for a Homeless Stanley 45 by Jim Harvey</title>
            <description>As far as I can tell, this particular 45 dates from the late 50s. Almost new! It was a Christmas present to myself.&lt;br /&gt;
Actually, I already had a 45 but dropped it onto the concrete garage floor. In a fit of despair, I bid on this 45 on eBay and won.&lt;br /&gt;
Meanwhile I was able to repair the cracked main stock on the first 45 so now I have two of them working. Neither came with an original box which was likely cardboard anyway. Hence this project. Guess I will have to build two of them.</description>
