        <item>
            <title>Skelton Dovetail Saw Review by Jim Hendricks</title>
            <description>First of all... huge thanks to Shane for the chance to have a look at this fine saw.&lt;br /&gt;
And fine it is… as in &quot;fine art&quot;.&lt;br /&gt;
