        <item>
            <title>Building a Saw Till by Jeff Strickland</title>
            <description>I finally decided that hanging all my saws from two hooks on the wall wasn&apos;t good enough any more, so I started on a saw till.&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
Dimensions are 24&quot; wide, 40&quot; tall. Basic, open style with slanted sides. The bottom is 6&quot; deep and I will build either two drawers and a cubby, or three drawers.</description>
