        <item>
            <title>The Sharp Priorities… by Matthew Cianci</title>
            <description>When it comes to teaching saw sharpening, I generally recommend students follow a hierarchy while developing their skills.&lt;br /&gt;
By suggesting where to focus their attention first, it helps new filers get their saws sharp and cutting true with the shortest learning curve.&lt;br /&gt;
